2:T733,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Designs.ai better than Galileo AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Designs.ai scores 6.0 overall while Galileo AI scores 7.0. Designs.ai is best for small businesses and marketers, while Galileo AI excels for designers seeking inspiration and product teams."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Designs.ai or Galileo AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Designs.ai starts at $29/mo and Galileo AI starts at $19/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Designs.ai to Galileo AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Designs.ai and Galileo AI support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Designs.ai vs Galileo AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Designs.ai holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Galileo AI has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Designs.ai for multiple design tools in one platform and Galileo AI for impressive ai-generated ui quality."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Designs.ai or Galileo AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Galileo AI for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Designs.ai remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize multiple design tools in one platform. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__