c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Designs.ai and Galileo AI share a solid foundation of core features including Ai Generation, Export Formats. Where Designs.ai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Templates and Drag And Drop and Brand Kit and Animations and Stock Assets, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Galileo AI uniquely offers Responsive, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Designs.ai holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Galileo AI scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Galileo AI comes in at a lower starting price of $19/mo, while Designs.ai begins at $29/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
