10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Designs.ai is best suited for small businesses, marketers, non designers, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Galileo AI, meanwhile, shines for designers seeking inspiration, product teams, rapid ideation, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2019, Designs.ai describes itself as \"All-in-one AI creative platform for logos, videos, mockups, and copy.\" Galileo AI, established in 2022, positions itself as \"AI design tool that generates editable UI designs from text prompts.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Galileo AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), more competitive pricing. However, this does not mean Designs.ai is a poor choice — far from it. Designs.ai excels in its own right, particularly for small businesses and marketers.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value impressive ai-generated ui quality, go with Galileo AI. If multiple design tools in one platform matters more to you, Designs.ai is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
